data.value:
Together Culture is making space to create, connect and to become more creative.
Join our burgeoning community of open-minded and curious people and make 5 Ftizroy Street your home away from home.
Benefits include: Inclusive tickets to all events Inclusive tickets to all collaborative & creative skills development workshops A City Centre base that you can call home, have a (free) coffee with your friends, host your next bookclub, do some work, be inspired, or just be. Participation in the annual Citizens’ Studio A voice in decision about new social enterprises developed in Together Culture’s incubator. A first edition Together Culture ‘Living Book’ - a digital workbook for living the values that emerged through co-design to bring creative practice into all your endeavours.
